<h2 id="remarks">Remarks</h2><p>The default font mapper is used by any TextBlocks that don't
have an explicit font mapper set (see the <a href="./../ref/Topten.RichTextKit.TextBlock.FontMapper">TextBlock.FontMapper</a> property).</p>
<p>Replacing the default font mapper allows changing the font mapping
for all text blocks that don't have an explicit mapper assigned.</p>

